data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of a serene GATED neighborhood! This spacious 6 bedroom, 4 bathroom POOL home with a MOTHER-IN-LAW SUITE offers 3192 square feet of luxurious living space, perfect for accommodating family and guests in comfort and style. NEW ROOF COMING SOON!  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the elegance of a raised dining room featuring mosaic tile flooring and a tray ceiling, seamlessly connecting to the outdoor oasis through sliders leading to the pool area. The pool bath, adorned with a walk-in shower, wood vanity, and a copper sink, offers convenience and style with direct access to the pool area.  The master bedroom is a retreat in itself, boasting wood-look tile floors and double French doors with blind inserts that open to the pool area. The accompanying master bath is a spa-like haven, complete with tile flooring, double vanities, a walk-in shower, a deep soaking tub, and his and hers closets, ensuring ample space for all your wardrobe needs.  Prepare culinary delights in the gourmet kitchen equipped with a large island featuring a cooktop, tile backsplash, trash compactor, stainless steel refrigerator, built-in microwave and oven, farm sink, and SOLID SURFACE countertops. Adjacent to the kitchen is a cozy breakfast nook with a seamless bay window, perfect for enjoying morning coffee.  Entertain with ease in the large family room featuring two sets of sliders leading to the pool area, seamlessly integrating indoor and outdoor living spaces. Relax and unwind in the solar-heated screened-in chlorine pool surrounded by a spacious lanai, ideal for hosting gatherings or enjoying quiet evenings under the stars.  This home also features two secondary bedrooms with large closets connected to a bonus area with a built-in desk and wood-look tile floors, along with a Jack and Jill bathroom boasting double vanities and a separate room for the toilet and shower.   The laundry room is inside the home and offers convenience with built-in cabinets and a utility sink, while the 2-car garage provides ample storage space with a large attic area.  Additionally, this property includes an attached mother-in-law suite featuring a living area, dining area, bedroom with pocket doors to the living area for privacy, two closets, and a kitchen with new appliances, tile flooring, a pass-through to the family room, and a bathroom with double vanities and a tiled walk-in shower.  With new fans and lights throughout, this meticulously designed home offers comfort, convenience, and luxury at every turn. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own and experience the epitome of modern living!
